title: Someone Comes To Kill Me
alternative_title: 誰かが殺しにやってくる ; Dareka ga Koroshi ni Yatte Kuru
status: 誰かが殺しにやってくる ; Dareka ga Koroshi ni Yatte Kuru
description:
Description :
        It's been three years since that incident when classmate bullying pushed a lone girl over the edge? One day, however, someone with the same name as one of those classmates is killed. When Emiko hears the news of the person who shared her name, she suddenly becomes uneasy and on edge. She recalls that before her death, the girl proclaimed to Emiko, ?You will be the sixth who I will curse.? Has her turn finally come?!
A spine-chilling collection of psycho horror stories!
